text: Are you ready for back-to-school shopping? Create a game plan to make the experience fun rather than stressful. Here's where to start.

text: Your Ultimate Buying Guide to the Best Backpacks
label: n

text: One of the key items on most back-to-school shopping lists are backpacks for school. And not just any backpacks, but cool backpacks for school, right? Your goal may be to find one that will be both versatile and rugged.

text: A Guide to Finding the Right Calculator
label: n

text: One of the hardest things to shop for during back-to-school shopping season may be a calculator. After all, there are scientific calculators, graphic calculators and basic calculators. And they come with all sorts of bells and whistles and at different price points.
label: n

text: While back-to-school shopping can be a lot of fun, stocking up for a new school year can also get pretty pricey. Thankfully, back-to-school sales offer deep discounts on a range of common school supplies, and nothing says “welcome back to school” quite like getting a great deal.
label: n

text: Back-to-school shopping sales typically begin during the summer months, giving families plenty of time before school starts up again. To stay on top of potential deals, shoppers should keep an eye out for sales starting in July. For customers who prefer to skip busy stores during the back-to-school season, excellent discounts are also available online during this time.
label: n

text: What should I include on my back-to-school shopping list?
label: n

text: Teachers often provide detailed school supply lists to help families complete their back-to-school shopping. While these back-to-school lists can be hugely helpful, they may not include all the items necessary for a successful school year.
label: n

text: For example, parents may want to buy a new lunch box and food containers during their school shopping, setting their child up to enjoy nutritious meals. Additionally, back-to-school shopping can involve purchasing new gadgets, such as a laptop computer or tablet tailored to students . Back-to-school deals are also available in these categories, so it’s a great time to shop for these kinds of items.
label: n

text: How will back-to-school shopping be different in 2021
label: n

text: The COVID-19 pandemic caused schools and families to adopt new learning methods , with differing approaches emerging around the country. The 2021 back-to-school season may still reflect many of these changes, causing students and teachers to shop differently than they have in years past.
label: n

text: For example, parents might be asked to add hand sanitizer to their back-to-school shopping lists or purchase technology necessary for virtual learning. Thankfully, back-to-school sales will likely include all the items necessary to make students safe and successful.
